 利用下拉選單設定切割起點【Edit】&rarr;【Set Maker A】、切割終點【Edit】&rarr;【Set Maker B】<br />\n2) 左邊「Format」下拉選單是輸出的格式要選對（跟你輸入的格式一樣）<br />\n3) 再利用【File】&rarr;【Save】&rarr;【Save Video】將切割的片段另存新檔（自行輸入一樣的副檔名）<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.azofreeware.com/2010/05/avidemux-252.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.azofreeware.com%2F2010%2F05%2Favidemux-252.html&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=ba5b1fba\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.azofreeware.com/2010/05/avidemux-252.html</a>"}]}